## Dependency rules

- Lower layers (types, config) may not import from higher layers (service, ui).
- Cross-cutting concerns (auth, logging, telemetry) flow through a Provider,
  not direct calls.
- Violations are detected by `scripts/check-architecture.sh` (advisory by default).

